  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is making use of school policy- recess outside classroom (ROC7-11)
      for increasing the time spent outdoor during recess and encouraging children spent time
      outdoor up to 11 hours in each week to investigate the vision change, myopia onset and
      progression in these schoolchildren.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
